    {
        "content": "<p>so maybe just wait until it has been upstreamed.</p>",
        "id": 407237397,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1702300245
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Also the change seems a little odd to me, since you changed the call to <code>get_current</code> in the definition of <code>fn current()</code> which is used by <code>current!()</code>. This will lead to nontermination. I also think <code>ptr</code> should be named <code>as_ptr</code> and it should return a raw pointer to <strong>this</strong> task, not a reference to the current task.</p>",
        "id": 407237812,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1702300418
    }
]